	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, May 2nd 8:24 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Are you distressed on the idea of being useless after 50,<br>Hate the idea of being a mana dumping death drager?<br>Well here are some facts to chear up you up,<br><br>1. Druid get it as bad as we do at 50+<br>Go to the druid Board and check out how many people whine about how BORING it is the play a druid post 50...<br>2. Clerics for example, there life post 50+ consides of sitting on their a$$e$ all day staring at their spell book, Fun?, think not.<br>3.Enchanters- Unless they have Anon on for their entire life, they will have newbies asking them for Clerity or Breeze forever.<br>4.Wizards(Nukers)- Once agian another spell book existance... Their lives are almost as boring as a clerics... But they get the bonus of hitting the crap out of monsters( Downside, Agro HELL)<br>5. Bards- Lalala, thats the sound they make when their fingers start to bleed, Twisting is SOOOO boring... (twisting is singing up to 4-5 songs at once)(hard to do, but very boring)They are weaker than Warriors and all they have after that is songs.<br>6. Warriors- Swing,Kick,Bash,Miss,Kick,Miss, Nuf sayed.<br>7. Rogue- Pierce Pierce pierce, BACKSTAB, Pierce. Nuf sayed.<br><br>Well there you have it, Don't look down on death, look happy, be evil, Kill stuff. HAVE FUN<br><br>Skwy Midget Death raiser(Gnome Necro)<br>17th corpse<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
